[It seems at present that the earlier suspicions of blue green algae
being involved in SCI cases could not be confirmed. Information on the
actual etiology of the syndrome, which has gained public attention
mainly because of its relevance to the Queen's Sandringham estate and
her dogs, is awaited. - Mod.AS

